      <h2>Before you apply</h2>

<p>You need to <a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/modes/driving/account-create-account-29278">create a London Road User Charging account</a>. (Already have an account? <a href="https://reg.tflcc.co.uk/TFL.LRUC.AccountAuth/S1">Sign in</a> now.)</p>

<p>Then, to set up Auto Pay, you will need your:</p>

<ul>
	<li>Vehicle registration details</li>
	<li>Bank or payment card details</li>
</ul>

<h3>Annual charge</h3>

<p>The &pound;10 registration charge for each vehicle added to Auto Pay must be paid every year. You don't have to pay this charge immediately - it will be added to your first statement.</p>
      
           
      

